Jill Turner

Jill Turner is an Application Architect at Mayo Clinic with over 16 years of Epic software implementation experience. She loves to run, Peloton (@jillecat), and eat brussel sprouts. She lives in Fairfax Station, VA with her Army Husband Dusty and two kids Cal (8) and Reese (6).

Education

B.A. Political Science and Economics | Michigan State University: August 2000 - May 2004
